{\b1 \cf21 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs24 \li0 
{\b1 \cf21 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs24 \sa0 \sb0 
After Proceedings Begin
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
When representing a plaintiff, counsel may provide the client with negotiation leverage by beginning formal court proceedings and demonstrating through the filing that the client is serious about pursuing its rights. Through the complaint, counsel should articulate the strength of the claims in clear terms.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
From a defendant\rquote s perspective, by waiting to engage in a settlement dialogue until after court proceedings begin, counsel:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 {\fi-360 \li {\*\pn \pnlvlblt \ilvl0 \ls46 \pnindent0 \pnf1 {\f2 \pntxtb \u8226\'3f}}{\listtext \b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 \u8226\'3f\tab }\ls46 {\pntext }
{\pard }\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \ql \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa180 \sb160 
Force the plaintiff to commit to the process and incur the expense of preparing, filing, and serving the complaint.
\par {\pntext }
}
}
}
}{\fi-360 \li {\*\pn \pnlvlblt \ilvl0 \ls47 \pnindent0 \pnf1 {\f2 \pntxtb \u8226\'3f}}{\listtext \b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 \u8226\'3f\tab }\ls47 {\pntext }
{\pard }\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \ql \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa180 \sb160 
Learn whether the plaintiff was bluffing about its litigation intentions.
\par {\pntext }
}
}
}
}{\fi-360 \li {\*\pn \pnlvlblt \ilvl0 \ls48 \pnindent0 \pnf1 {\f2 \pntxtb \u8226\'3f}}{\listtext \b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 \u8226\'3f\tab }\ls48 {\pntext }
{\pard }\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \ql \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa180 \sb160 
Obtain the opportunity to assess the scope, nature, and strength of the plaintiff\rquote s claims before engaging in a settlement dialogue.
\par {\pntext }
}
}
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri90 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li90 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb180 
Once a client realizes these initial benefits, counsel should assess the probability that the client ultimately may settle. Depending on the strength of each party\rquote s claims and defenses and the extent of damages apparent at the pleading stage, the parties may benefit from quickly reaching a settlement and finalizing the terms before the parties incur additional legal costs and become further entrenched in their positions.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
However, waiting to start negotiating settlement until after litigation starts can negatively impact the potential for settlement, as either or both of the parties may not want to discuss settlement immediately after proceedings formally begin.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
