{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
Discovery is often the most expensive part of litigation. The costs increase with each phase of the discovery process, including the costs of bringing and defending against motions to compel discovery responses. Counsel should:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li0 {\fi-360 \li {\*\pn \pnlvlblt \ilvl0 \ls49 \pnindent0 \pnf1 {\f2 \pntxtb \u8226\'3f}}{\listtext \b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 \u8226\'3f\tab }\ls49 {\pntext }
