{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \ql \fs18 \li480 
{\b0 \cf19 \f0 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs18 \sa180 \sb160 
Compare and factor into the settlement analysis each party\rquote s relative discovery burdens. There may be no strategic or financial advantage to incurring the expense of discovery only to engage in a settlement dialogue immediately after completing this stage of the litigation.
\par {\pntext }
}
}
}
}{\fi-360 \li {\*\pn \pnlvlblt \ilvl0 \ls50 \pnindent0 \pnf1 {\f2 \pntxtb \u8226\'3f}}{\listtext \b0 \cf19 \f0 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs18 \li480 \u8226\'3f\tab }\ls50 {\pntext }
